You will find that you can add an optional fallback image for the gravatar images.

{noformat}
<img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/00000000000000000000000000000000?d=identicon" />
Or using github identicon:
<img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/00000000000000000000000000000000?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F00000000000000000000000000000000.png" />
{noformat}
It would take 5 mins to implement this feature and it does not add any security risks if you re-use the gravatar ID.

